description:
For owners of MLB® The Show™ 23 Standard Edition only. MLB® The Show™ 23 game NOT INCLUDED with this Add-On product.

Your purchase of Deluxe Add-On grants you:

• Five Gold Choice packs.
• 20 The Show packs.
• One Ballplayer pack.
• Double daily login rewards.
• 25K Stubs™.
